{
  "stem": "7455.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They wanted that piece for their cigarette.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So with a stick, they tried to reach for it, I saw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Scrape-- they almost got it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And finally they got it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They opened it up with a piece of newspaper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They spread that tobacco far.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when they lit it-- it was like a flame-- everybody had a smoke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES] They were bringing them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They lined them up by the kitchen to stand in line with their pack that they have to pour in some soup with worms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And near the kitchen there, there was like a garbage pile where the cook threw out the peels and garbage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So one of the soldiers, while in line, went over and picked some of this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were starving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The cook saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "With a big cane, he went over and started hitting him and hitting him-- he was lying down-- kicking and hitting and hitting him until he didn't move anymore.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They dragged him away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You saw the faces of the other soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That is prison, and those were the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "This cook-- if he was a cook, he was not in the military, but he was cruel and hateful.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was a terrible experience for us to see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we worked there for some time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then, they were leaving, going forward, the-- the whole group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't know what they did with the prisoners, but they announced that they are moving on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were moving it more towards Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't know if they killed the prisoners, if they bothered keeping them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So our job was finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was necessary-- they were catching now young men to work in the streets and houses, taking them out.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
